<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kiker's U-Pull-It — Icon Set Comparison</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Saira:ital,wght@0,600;0,700;0,800;1,700;1,800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<!-- Phosphor (regular + bold + fill) -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@phosphor-icons/web@2.1.1/src/regular/style.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@phosphor-icons/web@2.1.1/src/bold/style.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@phosphor-icons/web@2.1.1/src/fill/style.css">
<!-- Tabler -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@3.24.0/dist/tabler-icons.min.css">
<style>
:root{
  --red:#DC161F;--red-700:#B4101A;--amber:#F6A100;--amber-600:#D98200;--ink:#0B0611;
  --bg:#F4F4F6;--surface-3:#EFEFF1;--text:#0B0611;--text-2:#55555B;--text-3:#86868D;
  --line:#E5E5E8;--line-2:#D8D8DC;--green:#1E9E57;--green-700:#0F6E3B;--green-wash:#E4F5EC;--green-line:rgba(15,110,59,.22);
  --grad-ink:linear-gradient(160deg,#0B0611,#1A1719);--grad-red:linear-gradient(135deg,#DC161F,#8C0C14);
  --r-md:4px;--r-lg:6px;--r-pill:100px;--e1:0 1px 2px rgba(11,6,17,.08);--e2:0 8px 20px rgba(11,6,17,.10);
  --display:'Saira',system-ui,sans-serif;--body:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;--mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--body);line-height:1.6}
h1,h2,h3{margin:0;font-family:var(--display);font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:-.01em;line-height:1.05}
.wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px}
.eyebrow{font-family:var(--body);font-weight:600;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.eyebrow::before{content:"";width:18px;height:2px;background:var(--red)}
.lead{color:var(--text-2);max-width:64ch;margin:10px 0 0}
.note{background:#FFF4DC;border:1px solid #FFC74D;border-left:4px solid var(--amber);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:14px 16px;font-size:14px;margin:18px 0}
.doc-h{border-left:4px solid var(--red);padding:4px 0 4px 16px;margin:46px 0 14px}
.doc-h h2{font-style:italic;font-size:24px}.doc-h p{margin:4px 0 0;color:var(--text-2);font-size:14px}

/* comparison grid */
.cgrid{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden}
.cgrid th,.cgrid td{padding:14px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);text-align:center}
.cgrid thead th{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;font-family:var(--display);font-style:italic;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.03em}
.cgrid tbody th{text-align:left;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--text);background:var(--surface-3);width:200px}
.cgrid .ico{font-size:30px;color:var(--ink);line-height:1}
.cgrid svg.lucide{width:30px;height:30px;stroke:var(--ink);vertical-align:middle}
.cgrid tr:last-child td,.cgrid tr:last-child th{border-bottom:none}
.cap{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:4px}

/* weights */
.weights{display:flex;gap:30px;flex-wrap:wrap;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:24px}
.weights .w{text-align:center}.weights .w .ico{font-size:40px;color:var(--ink)}.weights .w .l{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:6px}

/* in-context */
.ctx-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
.ctx{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden}
.ctx .hd{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;font-family:var(--display);font-style:italic;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:13px;padding:10px 16px;text-align:center}
.ctx .bd{padding:18px}
.trust{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:14px}
.trust .item{text-align:center}
.trust .item .ico{font-size:26px;color:var(--red)}.trust .item svg.lucide{width:26px;height:26px;stroke:var(--red)}
.trust .item .n{font-family:var(--display);font-style:italic;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;margin-top:4px}
.trust .item .s{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-2)}
.btn{margin-top:16px;width:100%;font-family:var(--display);font-weight:700;font-style:italic;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;font-size:13px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;height:44px;border-radius:var(--r-md);border:none;background:var(--red);color:#fff;cursor:pointer}
.btn .ico{font-size:17px}.btn svg.lucide{width:17px;height:17px;stroke:#fff}
@media(max-width:820px){.ctx-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

/* color treatments */
.swatches{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.sw{width:78px;height:78px;border-radius:var(--r-lg);display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:34px;border:1px solid var(--line)}
.sw.ink{background:#fff;color:var(--ink)}.sw.red{background:#fff;color:var(--red)}.sw.amber{background:#fff;color:var(--amber-600)}
.sw.green{background:var(--green-wash);color:var(--green-700);border-color:var(--green-line)}
.sw.ondark{background:var(--grad-ink);color:#fff}
	.pick{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:18px 20px;margin-top:14px;font-size:14px}
	code{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px;background:var(--surface-3);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px}
	.offline{display:none;background:#FDEDEE;border:1px solid #f5b5b8;color:#8C0C14;border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:12px 14px;font-size:13px;margin:14px 0}
	.mini-footer{background:var(--ink);color:rgba(255,255,255,.74);margin-top:30px}
	.mini-footer .wrap{padding-top:30px;padding-bottom:30px}
	.mini-footer .footer-logo{display:inline-flex;background:#fff;border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:8px 10px;width:230px;max-width:100%;line-height:0;margin-bottom:18px}
	.mini-footer .footer-logo img{display:block;width:100%;height:auto}
	.mini-footer h2{font-size:18px;font-style:italic;color:#fff;margin-bottom:14px}
	.mini-footer .links{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:20px}
	.mini-footer h3{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-bottom:10px}
	.mini-footer a{display:block;color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:7px;text-decoration:none}
	.mini-footer a:hover{color:#fff}

/* ===== RESPONSIVE HARDENING (added) — desktop·laptop·tablet·mobile ===== */
html{-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%}
body{overflow-x:hidden}
img,svg,video,iframe{max-width:100%;height:auto}
.wrap{width:100%;padding-left:clamp(16px,4vw,24px);padding-right:clamp(16px,4vw,24px)}
.mono,.meta,.stock,.km,.k,.row-tag,.a2{overflow-wrap:anywhere}
table{max-width:100%}
@media(max-width:1024px){.plates,.fcards,.cs-grid,.whygrid,.why-cards,.rcards,.methods,.bcards,.deals,.cards3,.cards-row{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.sec{padding:60px 0}}
@media(max-width:768px){.hero-grid,.split2,.split2.top,.loc-grid,.area-grid,.svc-split,.prodgrid,.story-grid,.buy-grid,.owner,.paths,.vdp,.lead-grid,.embed .wrap,.contact-grid,.rules-grid,.buy-grid,.duo,.split,.cutaway{grid-template-columns:1fr}.cards-row,.cards3,.rcards,.methods,.bcards,.deals,.steps,.steps3,.tstats{grid-template-columns:1fr}.trustbar .wrap{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.buybox{position:static;top:auto}.finalcta .wrap{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;text-align:left}.oways{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px}.sec{padding:48px 0}}
	@media(max-width:560px){.fcards,.cs-grid,.whygrid,.why-cards,.rcards,.methods,.bcards,.deals,.cards3,.cards-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}.cta-row,.hero .cta-row,.grp,.finalcta .grp{flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch;width:100%}.cta-row>.btn,.grp>.btn,.finalcta .grp>.btn{width:100%}.qgrid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.qbar .qrow{flex-direction:column}.qbar .qrow .btn{width:100%}.gallery .thumbs{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}}
	@media(max-width:380px){.plates,.trustbar .wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
	@media(max-width:820px){.mini-footer .links{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}}
	@media(max-width:560px){.mini-footer .links{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <span class="eyebrow">Kiker's U-Pull-It · Icon Picker</span>
  <h1 style="font-style:italic;font-size:34px;margin:8px 0 4px">Pick the icon set</h1>
  <p class="lead">Same Kiker's icons, three professional open-source sets, side by side and in real components. All are free for commercial use and theme to brand color via <code>currentColor</code>. Pick the feel that fits the yard — then I wire it into the kit, and your custom "hero" icons drop in over it later.</p>
  <div class="offline" id="offline">⚠ Icons aren't loading — this page needs an internet connection to pull the icon sets from their CDNs. Reopen online.</div>
  <div class="note"><b>My lean:</b> a bolder, slightly industrial set reads better with Saira + the steel/NASCAR feel than a thin, delicate line set. <b>Phosphor Bold</b> and <b>Tabler</b> tend to fit; <b>Lucide</b> is cleaner/lighter. Trust your eye — that's what this page is for.</div>

  <div class="doc-h"><h2>Head to head</h2><p>Phosphor shown in its Bold weight.</p></div>
  <table class="cgrid">
    <thead><tr><th>Kiker's icon</th><th>Phosphor (Bold)</th><th>Tabler</th><th>Lucide</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody id="grid"></tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="doc-h"><h2>Phosphor weights</h2><p>If we go Phosphor, we can dial the weight. Bold or Fill suit the rugged brand.</p></div>
  <div class="weights">
    <div class="w"><div class="ico"><i class="ph ph-truck"></i></div><div class="l">Regular</div></div>
    <div class="w"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-truck"></i></div><div class="l">Bold</div></div>
    <div class="w"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-fill ph-truck"></i></div><div class="l">Fill</div></div>
    <div class="w" style="margin-left:20px"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-currency-dollar"></i></div><div class="l">Bold $</div></div>
    <div class="w"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-fill ph-shield-check"></i></div><div class="l">Fill shield</div></div>
    <div class="w"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-wrench"></i></div><div class="l">Bold wrench</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-h"><h2>In context</h2><p>The same trust bar + button, built with each set and brand color.</p></div>
  <div class="ctx-grid">
    <div class="ctx"><div class="hd">Phosphor Bold</div><div class="bd">
      <div class="trust">
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-lightning"></i></div><div class="n">Same-Day</div><div class="s">Pickup &amp; Cash</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-truck"></i></div><div class="n">Free</div><div class="s">Towing</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-shield-check"></i></div><div class="n">Done Right</div><div class="s">Paperwork</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-recycle"></i></div><div class="n">Recycled</div><div class="s">Responsibly</div></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn"><span class="ico"><i class="ph-bold ph-phone"></i></span>Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</button>
    </div></div>

    <div class="ctx"><div class="hd">Tabler</div><div class="bd">
      <div class="trust">
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ti ti-bolt"></i></div><div class="n">Same-Day</div><div class="s">Pickup &amp; Cash</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ti ti-truck"></i></div><div class="n">Free</div><div class="s">Towing</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ti ti-shield-check"></i></div><div class="n">Done Right</div><div class="s">Paperwork</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i class="ti ti-recycle"></i></div><div class="n">Recycled</div><div class="s">Responsibly</div></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn"><span class="ico"><i class="ti ti-phone"></i></span>Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</button>
    </div></div>

    <div class="ctx"><div class="hd">Lucide</div><div class="bd">
      <div class="trust">
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i data-lucide="zap"></i></div><div class="n">Same-Day</div><div class="s">Pickup &amp; Cash</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i data-lucide="truck"></i></div><div class="n">Free</div><div class="s">Towing</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i data-lucide="shield-check"></i></div><div class="n">Done Right</div><div class="s">Paperwork</div></div>
        <div class="item"><div class="ico"><i data-lucide="recycle"></i></div><div class="n">Recycled</div><div class="s">Responsibly</div></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn"><span class="ico"><i data-lucide="phone"></i></span>Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</button>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-h"><h2>Brand-color treatments</h2><p>Any set takes brand color via <code>currentColor</code> — example with Phosphor Bold.</p></div>
  <div class="swatches">
    <div class="sw ink"><i class="ph-bold ph-wrench"></i></div>
    <div class="sw red"><i class="ph-bold ph-wrench"></i></div>
    <div class="sw amber"><i class="ph-bold ph-wrench"></i></div>
    <div class="sw green"><i class="ph-bold ph-recycle"></i></div>
    <div class="sw ondark"><i class="ph-bold ph-wrench"></i></div>
  </div>

  <div class="pick">
    <b>Once you pick:</b> I replace every emoji across the pages with the chosen set, add it to the component kit as the official icon system (fixed size + <code>currentColor</code>), and set a drop-in convention so your custom hero icons (cash-for-cars, pull-parts, tow, recycle, done-right, 25-years) swap in 1:1 — no layout changes. Tell me the winner, or even mix: e.g., "Phosphor Bold everywhere."
  </div>
  <p style="margin-top:30px;color:var(--text-3);font-size:13px">Phosphor, Tabler, and Lucide are all open-source (MIT / ISC) and free for commercial use. Loaded from public CDNs for this preview only; the production site bundles just the chosen set.</p>
</div>

